about_bio.text: Hello, my name is Graeme and I am a full-stack web developer. I am working at Places4Students where I have helped develop a house rental .NET Core website by programming in the front-end and back-end.

In December I graduated from the Computer Programmer Analyst program at Niagara College where I’ve studied database, web and software development techniques. Through a school opportunity, I  have also helped create a messaging app for a non-profit organization with a team of students.
